AI is more than just technology, it’s a tool to help us reconnect with our values & put people at the centre of innovation.
From tackling inequality to driving inclusion and powering economic growth, AI can help us unlock solutions to Africa’s dev challenges. ~@ahunnaeziakonwa

Sharing outputs of a new study on #bioethanol adoption in #Tanzania with evidence-based assessment, providing insights for stakeholders who aim to drive Tanzania’s #cleancooking transition forward.
Working paper: https://mecs.org.uk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Unlocking-the-Potential-of-Bioethanol-in-Development-Setting-Contexts.pdf…
Briefing note: https://mecs.org.uk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Scaling-Up-Bioethanol-for-Clean-Cooking-in-Tanzania-Briefing-Note.pdf…

PRAISE THE LORD!

For a while now, My spirit's been telling me that my friends @clevabanking sent me money.

But in this economy, who wants to give you free money??

I checked my USD account now, lo and behold, shawarma is secured for my babe. 

Where is that her cleva tag sef
